Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:07.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ワタシを呼ぶのは誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:12.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}温もりに憧れ行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}One more time, time, time!
