Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}解除 Poker Face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}完全等身大の赤裸々Talkで
